    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;##Mysql Galera Cluster&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;###准备环境&lt;br&gt;修改网卡配置&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;修改hosts文件&lt;br&gt;    /etc/hosts&lt;br&gt;    192.168.3.101   db1&lt;br&gt;    192.168.3.102   db2&lt;br&gt;    192.168.3.103   db3&lt;br&gt;关闭防火墙及selinux&lt;br&gt;    /etc/init.d/iptables stop&lt;br&gt;    chkconfig iptables off&lt;br&gt;    setenforce 0&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;###Add MariaDB Repositories&lt;br&gt;    vi /etc/yum.repos.d/mariadb.repo&lt;br&gt;    [mariadb]&lt;br&gt;    name = MariaDB&lt;br&gt;    baseurl = &lt;a href=&quot;http://yum.mariadb.org/10.0/centos6-amd64&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;http://yum.mariadb.org/10.0/centos6-amd64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;    gpgkey=&lt;a href=&quot;https://yum.mariadb.org/RPM-GPG-KEY-MariaDB&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;https://yum.mariadb.org/RPM-GPG-KEY-MariaDB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;    gpgcheck=1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;###Install MariaDB Galera Cluster 10.0 software&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo yum install http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/x86_64/socat-1.7.2.3-1.el6.x86_64.rpm -y
sudo yum install MariaDB-Galera-server MariaDB-client rsync galera -y 
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;###Setup MariaDB security&lt;br&gt;    sudo service mysql start&lt;br&gt;    sudo /usr/bin/mysql_secure_installation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;###Create MariaDB Galera Cluster users （都操作）&lt;br&gt;    mysql -u root -p&lt;br&gt;    mysql&amp;gt; DELETE FROM mysql.user WHERE user=’’;&lt;br&gt;    mysql&amp;gt; GRANT ALL ON &lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt; TO ‘root’@’%’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘123456’;&lt;br&gt;    mysql&amp;gt; GRANT USAGE ON &lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt; to sst_user@’%’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘123456’;&lt;br&gt;    mysql&amp;gt; GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES on &lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt; to sst_user@’%’;&lt;br&gt;    mysql&amp;gt; FLUSH PRIVILEGES;&lt;br&gt;    mysql&amp;gt; quit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;###Create the MariaDB Galera Cluster config&lt;br&gt;    service mysql stop  #all host stop&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#####db1 conf&lt;br&gt;    cat &amp;gt;&amp;gt; /etc/my.cnf.d/server.cnf &amp;lt;&amp;lt; EOF&lt;br&gt;    binlog_format=ROW&lt;br&gt;    default-storage-engine=innodb&lt;br&gt;    innodb_autoinc_lock_mode=2&lt;br&gt;    innodb_locks_unsafe_for_binlog=1&lt;br&gt;    query_cache_size=0&lt;br&gt;    query_cache_type=0&lt;br&gt;    bind-address=0.0.0.0&lt;br&gt;    datadir=/var/lib/mysql&lt;br&gt;    innodb_log_file_size=100M&lt;br&gt;    innodb_file_per_table&lt;br&gt;    innodb_flush_log_at_trx_commit=2&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_provider=/usr/lib64/galera/libgalera_smm.so&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_cluster_address=”gcomm://192.168.3.101,192.168.3.102,192.168.3.103”&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_cluster_name=’galera_cluster’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_node_address=’192.168.3.101’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_node_name=’db1’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_sst_method=rsync&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_sst_auth=sst_user:123456&lt;br&gt;    EOF&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#####db2 conf&lt;br&gt;    cat &amp;gt;&amp;gt; /etc/my.cnf.d/server.cnf &amp;lt;&amp;lt; EOF&lt;br&gt;    binlog_format=ROW&lt;br&gt;    default-storage-engine=innodb&lt;br&gt;    innodb_autoinc_lock_mode=2&lt;br&gt;    innodb_locks_unsafe_for_binlog=1&lt;br&gt;    query_cache_size=0&lt;br&gt;    query_cache_type=0&lt;br&gt;    bind-address=0.0.0.0&lt;br&gt;    datadir=/var/lib/mysql&lt;br&gt;    innodb_log_file_size=100M&lt;br&gt;    innodb_file_per_table&lt;br&gt;    innodb_flush_log_at_trx_commit=2&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_provider=/usr/lib64/galera/libgalera_smm.so&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_cluster_address=”gcomm://192.168.3.101,192.168.3.102,192.168.3.103”&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_cluster_name=’galera_cluster’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_node_address=’192.168.3.102’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_node_name=’db2’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_sst_method=rsync&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_sst_auth=sst_user:123456&lt;br&gt;    EOF&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#####db3 conf&lt;br&gt;    cat &amp;gt;&amp;gt; /etc/my.cnf.d/server.cnf &amp;lt;&amp;lt; EOF&lt;br&gt;    binlog_format=ROW&lt;br&gt;    default-storage-engine=innodb&lt;br&gt;    innodb_autoinc_lock_mode=2&lt;br&gt;    innodb_locks_unsafe_for_binlog=1&lt;br&gt;    query_cache_size=0&lt;br&gt;    query_cache_type=0&lt;br&gt;    bind-address=0.0.0.0&lt;br&gt;    datadir=/var/lib/mysql&lt;br&gt;    innodb_log_file_size=100M&lt;br&gt;    innodb_file_per_table&lt;br&gt;    innodb_flush_log_at_trx_commit=2&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_provider=/usr/lib64/galera/libgalera_smm.so&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_cluster_address=”gcomm://192.168.3.101,192.168.3.102,192.168.3.103”&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_cluster_name=’galera_cluster’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_node_address=’192.168.3.103’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_node_name=’db3’&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_sst_method=rsync&lt;br&gt;    wsrep_sst_auth=sst_user:123456&lt;br&gt;    EOF&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;###Initialize the first cluster node&lt;br&gt;在db1 执行集群初始化&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;/etc/init.d/mysql start --wsrep-new-cluster
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;在db1查询状态&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;[root@db1 ~]# mysql -uroot -p -e&amp;quot;show status like     &amp;apos;wsrep%&amp;apos;&amp;quot;
